parameters:
Cheerful fisherman: 'Hahaha, ahh~ this drink really hits the
spot.'

A hearty fisherman: 'I can't do my job unless I eat plenty
of food!'

Traveling Goods Merchant: 'When you come here, it becomes a
hassle to return to the mainland.'
Innkeeper: Welcome! Please make sure to try our seafood!

Innkeeper: Welcome to Beach Lepton! We have the freshest
seafood dishes and the finest wine.

Mansion Butler: Thank you for coming. The handover should be
at Beach Lepton without any mistakes.
Clea: Has your son been found?

Mansion Butler: He hasn't arrived yet, but we have confirmed
that he is not staying anywhere.

Sophia the Priestess: Um, I don't mind... but is it not
possible for all of us to detain them and defeat the enemy
together?

Mansion Butler: The young master is very stubborn! And we
must not injure them during the detainment!

Mansion Butler: They're using magic even though they're
being detained!

Mansion Butler: They forget about being detained when
they're lured by food!

Mansion Butler: Even though they're being detained, they're
still attacking!
Thief Nora: It's amazing! I can see everything!
Mage Relm: I-I'm being made a fool of!

Mansion Butler: Above all, the young master has no
resistance to women. No matter how strong his will is, it is
meaningless in front of breasts.
Priestess Sophia: Oh my, you're quite unique, aren't you?

Mansion Butler: It's natural to wear swimsuits at the beach,
so please change into one and make contact with the young
master.

Mansion Butler: I will investigate the location where the
transaction will take place.

The markers are not displayed on the beach for the young
master Metoki. Please find him based on the butler's hints
and clothing.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mansion Butler: As for the young master's characteristics...
he has hair that is tinged with a bluish color, just like
our master.
